">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">dayd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Elif yine kaleyi i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ten fethetme derdinde. Bir </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ekilde naz</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ge</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">irmeyi ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor Can</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">a. Murat ise ne yaps</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n? Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">e yemek </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">smarlamaktan ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ka </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">kar yolu yok.</span></p>
