<p><img src="/uploads/editor/foto4-hapis.jpg" alt="Ayşeg&uuml;l koğuş ağası olursa..." width="1024" height="682" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Can, Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;&uuml; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rak</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">p Elif</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">in yan</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">na gidince bizim k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z yaln</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z kald</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. G</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k ki Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">İ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">svi</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">re </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ak</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">gibi k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z valla! Elinden her i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">geliyor. Yeni g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">revi de </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rs</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z kovar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rdquo; </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">olmak. Eve h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rs</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z girdi fakat onu Can san</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">p, onun anlayaca</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">dilden cevap vermek istedi. O k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;&ccedil;&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">c</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k boyuyla sa</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">lam bir tekme yap</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ış</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">t</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">p h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rs</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">etkisiz hale getirdi. Tabii Can Bey bu s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rada sevgilisiyle yemek yesin. Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n yard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">na Murat yeti</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ti. K</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zca</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eve kadar b</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rakt</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Bizim </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z Can da hemen k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zd</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">bu duruma. Ama i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">in asl</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı &ouml;ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">renince morard</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">biraz. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&Ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ok yap</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor bunu sonra tepetaklak oluyor i</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">te. </span></p>
