<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Ayn</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rs</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">İ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">smail Dede ve Mediha</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&rsquo;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">y</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">da soymaya kalk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nca bu sefer ka</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">amad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Tam da o s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rada eve gelmekte olan Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l h</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">rs</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yakalad</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. Art</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k bundan sonra Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l ve Mediha aras</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nda daha samimi g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nt</span><span sty