<p><!-- pagebreak --></p>
<p><img src="/uploads/editor/foto2-mediha_ismail_dede.jpg" alt="Mediha kendisini affettirdi. İ&ccedil;ten i&ccedil;e o da İsmail Dede&rsquo;yi seviyor." width="3648" height="2432" /></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yaln</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">z belirtmesem olmaz, oyuncu performanslar</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">na bak</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">nca Nurseli </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">İ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">diz fazlas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yla </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ne </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">k</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">yor. Di</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">er karakterler zaman zaman s</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">r</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">tsalar da o rol</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n hakk</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">veriyor. Hani kendisiyle </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">zel bir ba</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ğı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">m falan da yok ama Ay</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">eg</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l nas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l ki dizinin dinamosuysa, Nurseli </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">İ</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">diz de bize ger</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ccedil;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ek anlamda oyunculuk nas</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ı</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">l oluru g</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&ouml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">steren ki</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ş</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">i. Bu benim d</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">&uuml;ş&uuml;</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">ncem elbette.</span></p>
